data.meta_description: Andy RossBreaststroke - 2016-17 (Senior): All-MAC Academic Team... Swam in three events... Finished 13th in the 100-yard breaststroke at the MAC Championship...
data.text:
2016-17 (Senior): All-MAC Academic Team... Swam in three events... Finished 13th in the 100-yard breaststroke at the MAC Championships... Posted seven top-10 finishes...

2015-16 (Junior): All-MAC Academic Team…Won 200-yard breaststroke at Little Rock (2:08.98)…Six top five finishes over the course of the season…Top Saluki time in 400-yard individual medley (4:05.86)…Top five Saluki time in 5 different events.

2014-15 (Sophomore): Academic All-Mac Team…Competed in eight meets for the Salukis…Finished 16th in the 400-yard IM at the MAC Championships…Opened the 2014-15 season with a second place finish in the 200-yard IM and a third place finish in the 200-yard breaststroke at Evansville on 10/4/14…Earned a second place finish in the 400-yard IM against UALR/WUSTL…Closed the regular season with a second place finish in the 200-yard IM against Evansville.

2013-14 (Freshman): Competed in eight meets on the year...Won two events...First collegiate win came in the 200 breaststroke at Evansville...Posted seven top-five finishes.
